      "text": "（今日もリズノワは遅くまで練習か。BIG4になって）\n（しばらく経つけど、練習熱心なのは相変わらずだな）",
      "startTime": 5.323598668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "さっきのところ、今までで一番合いましたね！\nみなさん、忘れないうちにもう一回やってみませんか？",
      "startTime": 13.6552384694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（ん？　いつもの練習風景と少し違うような……）",
      "startTime": 17.5599096935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの莉央さん、すっごくかっこ良かったです！\nでも、左手の振りをもっとこうした方が……",
      "startTime": 26.3567124049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "そう、そうです！　最高の最高にかっこいいです！\nそんな、私が頼もしいだなんて……えへへ",
      "startTime": 35.5900457382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、こころ！　今のところ、なんかしっくり\nこなかったよね。一緒に葵さんに見てもらわない？",
      "startTime": 43.9567124049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（へぇ……愛が率先して練習を引っ張ってるのか）\n（BIG4になって、心境の変化があったみたいだな）",
      "startTime": 52.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
